 Score an apnea as obstructive if it meets apnea criteria and is associated with absent inspiratory effort throughout the entire period of absent airflow.

 Score an apnea as central if it meets apnea criteria and is associated with absent inspiratory effort throughout the entire period of absent airflow.

 Score an apnea as mixed if it meets apnea criteria and is associated with absent inspiratory effort in the initial portion of the event, followed by resumption of inspiratory effort in the second portion of the event.

