 Subjects once consented and entered into the study, will all have a two week baseline period in which they will use a nasal mask using an airview cpap machine (which records all data).

 After the two week period all will switch to a full face mask with half using the same CPAP pressure and half with a new cpap pressure derived from our formula for the final two weeks.

 Those placed in the randomized into a new pressure will have an experimental procedure of getting a new pressure.

 We expect the AHI of the controls to increase.

